venue.name: Nippori Station (日暮里駅)
venue.header: According to the Foursquare community, this place is a 6.0 out of 10.
venue.explanation: We take into account visits and input from our community. You'll see a number on places based off of ratings and tips written by people like you.

items.summary: Lots of people like this place

items.text: Walk toward Sendagi station and discover Yanaka, an old well preserved neighborhood. Leave the station by the West exit, turn left and keep your right as walking down the road.
谷中で猫目的でお越しになった方は駅でこのお散歩マップをもらおう ٩( ╹▿╹ )۶
常磐線と他の路線の乗り換えが激しい。上野行の電車はここで結構な人が降り、品川行の電車もある程度空きます。上野東京ラインの開通の関係かここから品川行に乗車する人も現れました。
